    var changedEvent = 'event_form.event_changed';

    return {

        subscribe: function(scope, callback) {
            var deregister = $rootScope.$on(changedEvent, callback);
            scope.$on('$destroy', deregister);  //destroy the listener when done
        },
        
        publish: function(data) {
            $rootScope.$emit(changedEvent, data);
        }
    };

}]]></script><sys_class_name>sp_angular_provider</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-05-04 18:23:03</sys_created_on><sys_id>a9db9d4107d301107a55fa4d7c1ed0d9</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>spEventPubSub</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Cloud Dimensions Events" source="x_snc_cloudevents">77108b70610813007f44e59882b97a67</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Cloud Dimensions Events">77108b70610813007f44e59882b97a67</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_angular_provider_a9db9d4107d301107a55fa4d7c1ed0d9</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-05-04 18:23:03</sys_updated_on><type>service</type></sp_angular_provider></record_update>
